summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending plat 226W, page 15, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property in Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 4 E.W.M. from Duplex Residence Medium Density (RD 7200) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone.
